Asmae Leghzaoui (Arabic; amụrụ n'abalị iri atọ n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1976) bụ onye Morocco na-agba ọsọ n'etiti
Ọ bụ onye egwuregwu Olimpik ugboro abụọ maka Morocco.

N'afọ 1999, Leghzaoui mere ọganihu na-agba ọsọ site n'imeziwanye mita 3000 nke onwe ya kacha mma site na nkeji ma mebie ihe ndekọ ụwa maka ọsọ ụzọ 10K. Ọ bụ onye nke asaa na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị dị mkpirikpi na afọ 1999 IAAF World Cross Country Championships, na-eduga ndị Moroccan na ọla nchara na asọmpi otu
N'okporo ụzọ, ọ gbara ọsọ na mita 10,000 na 1999 World Championships in Athletics, mana o nweghị ike ịmecha ọsọ ahụ
N'afọ 2000, ọ meriri Cinque Mulini cross country meet wee were aha 5000m track na afọ 2000 African Championships in Athletics n'ikpeazụ n'afọ ahụ.

O ritere ihe nrite ọla edo na 10,000 mita na ọlaọcha na 5000 mita na 2001 Mediterranean Games. Ọ nọchitere anya Morocco na afọ 2001 World Championships in Athletics wee bụrụ onye nke asaa na 10,000 m ikpeazụ
Ọ meriri New York Mini 10K na afọ 2002, na-etinye oge ndekọ. Ọ dara ule ọgwụ maka EPO na afọ 2003, mana mgbe a machibidoro ya iwu afọ abụọ, ọ laghachiri na asọmpi asọmpi okporo ụzọ mba ụwa.
Leghzaoui nwere ọtụtụ mmeri n'ọsọ n'okporo ụzọ na United States na Mee 2005, na-ewere utu aha na Lilac Bloomsday Run, Bay to Breakers na Freihofer's Run for Women
O nwetara ihe nrite ọlaọcha nke 5000 m na 10,000 m maka Morocco na 2005 Mediterranean Games
N'afọ 2007, ọ gbara nke iri na isii na 2007 World Championships
Ọ gbara ọsọ na 2008 Beijing Olympics mana o nweghị ike ịmecha na 10,000m. O nwere mmeri azụ azụ na azụ na National Capital Marathon na Ottawa site na afọ 2008 ruo 2009.
O meriri asọmpi ọkara marathon na afọ 2011 Marrakesh Marathon, mezue ọsọ ahụ na oge ndekọ asọmpi nke 1:10:47.
